name: Jet Space (itch) (Diego Escalante)
description:
Your fellow spacenauts' ship has crashed. Find it, repair it, and make your way back home.

Jet Space is a game made in one month for the Github Game Off game jam. 

Tools Used:

  • Unity
  • Aesprite
  • Audacity
  • Bfxr
  • Teenage Engineering PO-20
  • Teenage Engineering PO-16
  • Alex Peterson's Spacescape
